{"tid":988284,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"對住d餸菜影相係咩野原因","createTime":"2019-01-20T02:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T04:17:57.000Z","uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"97b966e665922785d64c9359fc7cf60e14a9f755","tid":988284,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"個人黎講甚少影相 至於對住食物就近乎無<br />\n只不過去旅行 公司 屋企 餐廳都會不斷有周邊既人影<br />\n我問過人 佢影完d 相真係會睇？佢又無乜點解答過<br />\n去d 貴少少既食店真係每餸必影 當然時不時食大家樂都見到有人出手<br />\n究竟點解會吸引你地去影"},{"pid":"9d9d28faf6d2eae1ca6a29aefcf3845c42326a34","tid":988284,"uid":191338,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:48:06.000Z","msg":"留住溫暖，速度，溫柔和憤怒"},{"pid":"b759e39f48d068d7afe7b0b3635b7b2af471f393","tid":988284,"uid":54524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"咁我答你，影完會睇，此post已完"},{"pid":"72ebb1a2d528d182e9eb574803d598c3fb5751e1","tid":988284,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"打卡 攞like 威威"},{"pid":"b02e4eea365196893d47b57254b421c023e689c7","tid":988284,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9d9d28faf6d2eae1ca6a29aefcf3845c42326a34","tid":988284,"uid":191338,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:48:06.000Z","msg":"留住溫暖，速度，溫柔和憤怒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"影相其實係咪演俾人睇果個影相動作"},{"pid":"6851504b8d03d29a7782ee3e333365762fee712e","tid":988284,"uid":19678,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"有時食快餐都影，可能話比朋友or男女朋友甚至老毛 ，我食緊咩野<br />\nwtsapp send 出去，唔洗電話交代<br />\n但只會快影，5 洗較咩光暗角度"},{"pid":"0ead89cea00409fcb5272af5f77a28426c385ce5","tid":988284,"uid":19678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6851504b8d03d29a7782ee3e333365762fee712e","tid":988284,"uid":19678,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"有時食快餐都影，可能話比朋友or男女朋友甚至老毛 ，我食緊咩野<b